{"type": "article", "id": 9201, "title": "May the 4th 星战日，哪些品牌用对了原力？", "description": "昨天，你被“May the 4th be with you！”刷屏了吗？", "date": "2015-05-05T14:18:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9690, "name": "星战"}, {"id": 234, "name": "社交网络"}, {"id": 65, "name": "营销"}], "category": 18, "author": 3926, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607171146mnKRovAUwtaY0igk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t昨天是什么节日？除了青年节，5 月 4 日还是“星战日”。这个梗来源于《星球大战》里尤达大师的一句名言：May the Force be with you！愿原力与你同在！谐音也就是 May the 4th 了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t星战系列电影自 1977 年上映至今，衍生出了大量周边，以及遍布世界的粉丝文化，影响力早已超出了电影本身。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t所以，尽管“星战日”是个非官方的节日，依然有很多品牌看中了星战的粉丝基础与影响力，在这一天围绕“星战日”做起了营销。我们从中挑选了一些大家比较熟悉的品牌：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171140rk4OPnyKzA79MFJY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.259375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171140RtSrEoNJdCGqyLch.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171140JMBjwRgDpQVkbHFd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171141gYZdzqoi6f4pmOUh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171142tROyueBiMhcFrs98.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171142g8iutY4GfJXDIyMB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t以及，基本啥事都会来露个脸的乐高：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171143Vrz3pPyHvfbWM48K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171144zL9vlQYPbSjfaFJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61860465\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071711440HXNnkQDfJpOwS75.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.215625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171145yWL5OsVx7IKNvMme.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03636364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>NASA </span>又调皮了：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171145B3rLPURE5GjehSIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}